.Language=English,English
.Options CtrlStartPosChar=^<wrap>

@Contents
$^#Memo#
 #The following keys may be used:#
     #Esc#        :  exit
     #Alt0-Alt9#  :  switch to another memo (also #Ctrl0-Ctrl9#)
     #ShiftF2#    :  save as... (the path may be changed)
     #F6#         :  rename the current memo (no path change)

 #Note:#
   Exiting and switching between memos automatically saves the current memo.
